channel.title: Changing website html to your own
channel.description:
Lots people have asked me for this so this is just a little help for you guys
Difficulty Level: 1
Things you will need : - Winrar ([url=http://download.cnet.com/WinRAR-32-bit/3000-2250_4-10007677.html] http://download.cnet.com/WinRAR-32-bit/3000-2250_4-10007677.html[/url]) - Free Webhost ([url=http://webs.com]webs.com[/url]) - Template to insert ([url=http://up.ht/KGKEKu]http://up.ht/KGKEKu[/url]) - A Brain
For webhost i will be showing you how to use it on webs.com webhost just watch as i do it now
First off you will need a template if you need a Runescape old style click the link above find others on your own I will be using my own template either way they are all the same
Follow the video below for the rest.
http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=n44ZkgJ2I40&feature=youtu.be
Hope this helped you
